        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1099111778" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer456058069931863313">Inspiring and gorgeous assemblage of Hansberry&apos;s writing, from scenes from unfinished plays to journal entries, to lists of her hopes and dreams. The world lost her far too soon.</span>
  <span id="freeText456058069931863313" style="display:none">Inspiring and gorgeous assemblage of Hansberry's writing, from scenes from unfinished plays to journal entries, to lists of her hopes and dreams. The world lost her far too soon.</span>
