        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780451159526" href="/book/show/853163.To_Be_Young_Gifted_and_Black">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/12148012-evan?shelf=non-fiction">non-fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/12148012-evan?shelf=plays">plays</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/12148012-evan?shelf=african-american">african-american</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/12148012-evan?shelf=autobiography-memoirs">autobiography-memoirs</a>, 
