<div id="review_1535163767" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1535163767" />
    <a title="Dawn" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/2501576-dawn"><img alt="Dawn" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1439417670p2/2501576.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1535163767?book_show_action=true">Feb 02, 2016</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Dawn" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Dawn" href="/user/show/2501576-dawn">Dawn</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780451159526" href="/book/show/853163.To_Be_Young_Gifted_and_Black">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1535163767" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3319992161986076751">Reading this book made me wish Lorraine Hansberry had lived long enough to pen her own memoir and write more of the work she had envisioned. Even though she is known for her work as a playwright, I yearn for more of her prose, more of her letters and art work, without so many excerpts from her plays. While I found some of the dramatic excerpts relevant in context, I found myself more moved by the narrative sections, maybe because they captured more of Hansberry in her own words. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

